help you enroll under the new york state of health or government benefits including medicaid child health plus  qualified health plan for more information call  manhattan or   queens optometry services which includes general eye care examination diagnosis treatment and management of diseases and disorders that affect your vision by appointment only nutrition counseling by certified dieticians by appointment only language access line at all sites to help translate for patients who speak languages that our staff does not speak patient portal will give you online access to easily communicate with your provider refill your medication request appointments request referrals request test results send a message to your provider and view your medical summary     �  charles b wang community health center privacy notice  annual reports   �� about us about us mission and vision our history our medical staff board and management ��our services internal medicine pediatric care obgyn dental care mental health social work health education additional services our medical staff payment pharmacy new patients ��health resources health materials community resources publications quit smoking program hepatitis b program ��news  events good health day workshops and events newsletter blog ��support us support us imagine the future campaign online donation events employer matching gift workplace federated appeal fundraise for us donate while you shop gift planning donor recognition annual reports                  textsize   annual reports             �  charles b wang community health center privacy notice  online donation   �� about us about us mission and vision our history our medical staff board and management ��our services internal medicine pediatric care obgyn dental care mental health social work health education additional services our medical staff payment pharmacy new patients ��health resources health materials community resources publications quit smoking program hepatitis b pro